Na so in yi kokarin shiga wannan matsayi, na kama kwallon, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna wasa da shi a koyaushe kamar yadda zan iya, don haka na yi kokarin samar da lokacin da zan iya, Sturridge ya fada wa LiverpoolFC.com.
