Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar mai cike da nishadi da aka bayar a ranar Talata ta sabon alkalin kotun kolin kasar, Brett Kavanaugh da kuma shaidar matarsa Christine Blasey Ford, wadda ta zarge shi da laifin lalata da aka yi a shekarun 1990s.
A daidai wannan lokaci, harkar siyasa ta ci gaba da taɓarɓarewa kuma gidajen talabijin sun dakatar da jadawalin su na yau da kullun don buga sabon labarai a ranar Juma'a: Jeff Flake, Sanata daga Arizona, ya gabatar da kudirin da zai ba FBI damar bincika tuhumar na mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade da giya kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire mata tufafinta a wani biki a makaranta.
Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin wata shaida mai ban sha'awa cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane da yawa sun kalli shari'ar fiye da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ya ce sun kalli ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ba da shawarar kallon tashoshin talabijin na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanai ba nan da nan ga sauran gidajen talabijin da suka nuna tambayoyin, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma tana yawan samun matsala wajen auna ra'ayin mutane game da ofisoshin.
Don kwatanta wannan, wannan taron yana kama da na wasan kwallon kafa ko na kyautar Oscar.
A cewar Nielsen, mafi yawan masu kallo a wannan rana sun kasance a tashar Fox News Channel, ko kuma miliyan 5.69 masu kallo a wannan tashar sun goyi bayan Kavanaugh sosai.
ABC ta zo ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1, NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94, MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52 a cewar Nielsen.
