LeBron zai buga wasan farko a San Diego Lakers ranar Lahadi
Masu sha'awar wasan da ke son ganin LeBron James ya buga wasan farko a Los Angeles Lakers sun yi saurin kammala jiransa.
Luke Walton, kocin Lakers, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Har yanzu ba a yanke shawarar tsawon lokacin da zai buga wasan ba.
"Zai wuce minti daya kuma ya rage na minti 48," Walton ya fada a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mike Trudell, mai ba da rahoto na Lakers ya ce a shafin Twitter cewa James zai yi wasa ne na dan lokaci.
Bayan kammala atisayen a farkon makon nan, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasanni shida na Lakers kafin a fara kakar wasa.
Ya ce, "A wannan lokaci na aiki, ba na bukatar buga wasannin kakar wasa don shirya kaina".
Lokaci na taron Trump a West Virginia da kuma tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai gudanar da taron zabe da dama, na farko a wannan karon a Wheeling, jihar West Virginia.
Yana daya daga cikin tarurruka biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, inda zai kuma tsaya a wurare masu kyau, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da sabon alkalin kotun kolin, Trump na kokarin gina goyon baya a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron zaben shugaban kasa a jihar West Virginia, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon taron a Intanet?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da zai fara da karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron da aka yi da Trump a West Virginia a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
A lokacin da ake zargin cewa ya yi lalata da wasu mutane, mai yiwuwa Trump ne zai gabatar da kara a gaban kotun kolin da ake tuhumar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun kolin.
Amma babban burin taron Trump shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu nasarar yin zabe mai wuya a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, sakonnin yakin neman zaben Trump sun ce wadannan tarurruka biyar, da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, an yi su ne don "cika masu sa kai da masu goyon baya a kan yadda 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma karawa rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattijai da majalisar dattijai", a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar wakilai yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shirin shugaban kasa, zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama da zai iya yi a lokacin da za a fara yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump da ba a bayyana sunansa ba.
Za a yi taron ne a gidan wasan Wesbanco da ke Wheeling, kuma ana sa ran magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania za su zo, kuma za a ba da rahoto daga Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
Taron na ranar Asabar zai zama ziyarar Trump ta biyu zuwa West Virginia a wannan watan, bayan da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a jihar a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana son ya taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar Sanata na Republican na West Virginia, amma ya ragu a cikin binciken.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi kokarin kara masa farin jini", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
