HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14%
Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV ko kuma masu ciwon daji.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a ƙasar.
An samu karin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kamu ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da yadda ake yi a dā.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yadu da sauri a wasu yankunan ƙasar Sin domin ba da jini da ke ɗauke da cutar.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya sake raguwa zuwa kusan babu, in ji ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ko kuma cutar ƙanjamau ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000 kowace shekara.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT ta kasar Sin.
An ba da izinin yin luwadi a kasar Sin tun shekara ta 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT.
Domin dokokin da ake bi a ƙasar, an ƙididdige cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna aure.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne domin rashin isasshen maganin hana al'aura a waɗannan ma'aurata.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani sashe na shirin magance cutar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya fallasa bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican, ta yi tir da "ƙarya mai haɗari" da kuma "ra'ayin rikici"
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar wakilai Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin da ake yi mata cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar wakilai uku a shafukan Wikipedia.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat daga Los Angeles ya ce wadannan maganganun sun fito ne daga 'yan adawa da shafukan yanar gizo na 'yancin 'yancin' yancin.
"Maƙaryaci, ƙarya da ƙarin munanan ƙaryace-ƙaryace", Waters ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a Twitter.
Bayanan da aka fallasa sun hada da adiresoshin da lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattijai Lindsey Graham daga South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu daga Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis daga wasu mutane da ba a san su ba a kan Capitol Hill yayin da ake sauraron sauraron karar da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun koli, kan zargin cin zarafin mata.
Likitan ya zo ne bayan da 'yan majalisar dattawa uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan sadarwa na Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ce adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano mai ba da bayanan ya danganta da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da bayanan wani ma'aikacinta, a cewar wani bayani daga Capitol Hill.
"Wannan tuhuma ba ta da tushe, kuma ƙarya ce", Waters ya ci gaba.
Abokina na - wanda ke da sirri da tsaro a yanzu saboda waɗannan zarge-zargen ƙarya - ba shi da alhakin wannan ɓoyewar bayanai.
Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ƙarya ce kwarai da gaske.
Bayanin Waters ya sami saurin sukar a yanar gizo, ciki har da tsohon wakilin gidan farin Ara Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda cike yake da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da kwarewar zama a majalisar.
Idan aka zargi wani ba tare da dalili ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Ba za mu yi tsayayya da wannan ba.
Kada ka yi tambaya game da dalilin da ya sa mai zargin yake yin hakan.
Dole ne a nuna kwanciyar hankali da tunani.
Fleischer ya yi kama da yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukarsa suka ce ya nuna rashin jin daɗi a shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman takarar Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Babban abu idan gaskiya ne", ya ce.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya sanar da hukumomi da jami'an tsaro game da wannan zargin.
Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano wadanda suka aikata wannan laifin, ta ci gaba, kuma za a tuhume su da aikata duk wani abu da ya kunyatar da kuma yi wa dukkan ma'aikatana barazana.
Hoton bidiyon Johnny English Strikes Again - fim din leken asiri da Rowan Atkinson ya nuna cewa ba shi da ƙarfi
A yau, ya zama al'ada a nemi Brexit a duk wani sabon fim da aka yi da ya shafi tarihin Burtaniya, kuma wannan ya bayyana a cikin wannan farfadowar fim din Johnny English - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake farfadowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin wannan wasan kwaikwayon na wasan kwaikwayo na yadda muke da mummunar mummunar zama sabon kayan aiki ga kasar?
Ko da hakan gaskiya ne ko a'a, an sake ba Johnny English izinin yin abin da bai dace ba, kuma sunansa ya nuna cewa shi mai zane ne da aka tsara don a nuna a wasu ƙasashe da ba Turanci ba.
Shi ne, ba shakka, mai basira mai basira wanda yake nuna cewa yana da ban sha'awa amma yana da wani nau'i na Clouseau, da Mr. Bean da kuma ɗan ƙaramin ɗan adam wanda ya buga waƙa guda don "Chariots of Fire" a bikin bude gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
An kuma fara shi ne daga mai tafiya da kuma ɗan ƙasa mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin fim a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard da aka manta, inda ya fahimci komai a cikin rikici.
Akwai abu daya ko biyu masu kyau a cikin wannan sabon fim din Johnny English.
Na ji daɗin kallon Johnny English yana tafiya a kan jirgi mai saukar ungulu da ya saka rigar da ta yi kama da na dā.
Atkinson ya nuna kwarewar wasan kwaikwayo, amma wasan kwaikwayo yana da rauni kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman ma a lokacin da fina-finai masu mahimmanci kamar James Bond da kuma Mission Impossible suna ba da dariya.
Abin dariya ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma na ga cewa Johnny English ya shiga cikin wani abu mai ban mamaki da kuma mai ban sha'awa kamar Atkinson a cikin Mr. Bean.
Wannan fim din yana nuna cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani ɗan damfara ya shiga cikin asirin 'yan leƙen asirin ƙasar Biritaniya kuma ya gano dukan 'yan leƙen asirin ƙasar, musamman ma wanda yake lura da ayyukan leƙen asirin - amma abin baƙin ciki, Kevin Eldon ba shi da matsayi mai girma a wannan aikin.
Wannan shi ne matakin karshe ga Firayim Minista mai girman kai da rikice-rikice kuma a halin yanzu yana cikin babban hadari saboda manyan abokan adawar siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin mafi kyau a matsayinta na wanda ya kamata ya tuna da Theresa May, amma rubutun ba shi da yawa ga kifi.
Masu ba ta shawara sun gaya mata cewa duk masu leken asiri suna cikin haɗari kuma dole ne ta sami wanda ya riga ya zauna a kan dutse mai tsarki.
Kuma a nan ne Johnny English ya zo cikin labarin, yanzu shugaban makaranta a wata makaranta mai kyau, amma kuma yana ba da darussan sirri game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: ga wasu ban dariya da Turanci ya bayar game da makarantar leƙen asiri wanda ke tunatar da fim ɗin School of Rock.
An kira Turanci zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa kuma ya sadu da Bough, tsohon abokin aikinsa, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu mutum ne mai aure, matarsa mai kula da jirgin ruwa, amma a cikin wannan rawar da Vicki Pepperdine ba ta iya haskakawa ba.
Yanzu, 'yan leken asirin da ke yin duk abin da ya dace a hidimar Sarauniyarsu sun sake komawa cikin wasan kwaikwayo, kuma sun sake saduwa da Ophelia Bulletova, mai suna Olga Kurylenko.
A lokaci guda kuma, Firaministan kasar na cikin wata al'ajabi da wani mai kudi mai kudi mai yawa a masana'antar kere kere da ke da'awar zai iya magance matsalar kwamfuta ta kasar Birtaniya: wannan shi ne Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara tafiya: suna cin abinci a cikin gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai kyau tare da masu ba da abinci, suna yin mummunan aiki yayin da suke shiga cikin jirgin ruwa mai daraja na Volta, kuma Turanci ya juya kome a baya lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da gilashin gilashi na gaskiya don gano abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Babu wani abu da za a iya ragewa a wannan ƙarshen fim ɗin, amma ko da yake fim ɗin yana da ƙarfi sosai, amma a cikinsa babu wani abu da ya nuna cewa shi yaro ne.
Yana da kyau sosai.
Kuma kamar yadda na yi a fina-finan Johnny English, ba zan iya guje wa tunani ba: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da ta dace da baiwarsa?
Kungiyar kwadago ta musanta cewa tana shirin samar da makonni hudu na aiki ga Burtaniya, tare da albashi daya da na kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour karkashin jagorancin Jeremy Corbyn, tana kan wani tsari na musamman wanda zai baiwa 'yan Birtaniya damar yin aiki kwanaki hudu a mako, amma a biya su biyar.
An ce jam'iyyar tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su yi amfani da kuɗin da aka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha, kuma ma'aikata su more ƙarin hutu.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikaci ya sami hutu na kwana uku ba tare da rage albashinsa ba.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi zai "dace" da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma manufofinta na inganta ayyukan ma'aikata.
Kungiyar kwadago ta Trades Union Congress ta goyi bayan rage wa'adin aiki na kwana hudu, a matsayin wata hanya da ma'aikata za su yi amfani da sauyin tattalin arziki.
Wani jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa: "An shirya sanar da wani sabon tsarin mulki kafin karshen shekara.
Ba za a samu canji cikin dare ba, amma aikin kwana hudu a mako wata manufa ce da ta dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na sauya tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma manufofin jam'iyyar gaba daya.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce jam'iyyar farko da za ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, amma jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki kwana hudu a mako a yakin neman zaben ta na 2017.
Amma, jam'iyyar Labour ba ta goyi bayan wannan manufa.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: Ba a rubuta a cikin manufofin jam'iyyarmu cewa za a yi aiki na kwanaki hudu a mako ba kuma ba ma tunanin yin hakan.
John McDonnell, ministan kasuwanci na ofishin shadow, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa game da juyin juya halin zamantakewa a cikin tattalin arziki.
Mr. McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar dawo da iko daga "shugabannin da ba a sani ba" da kuma "masu tara kayan lambu" na kamfanonin abinci.
Shadow Ministan ya kuma ce masu hannun jarin kamfanonin ruwa na yanzu ba za su iya samun dukkan rabonsu ba, domin gwamnatin Labour na iya yin 'ƙiyayya' saboda aikata laifi.
