Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun ce a cikin minti 60 ko binciken FBI kan Kavanaugh zai iya canza ra'ayinsu
Binciken da FBI ke yi kan zargin da aka yi wa Alkalin Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh ya janyo cikas a zaben da aka yi na zaben babban alkalin kotun, kuma ya tayar da tambayar ko sakamakon binciken zai sa 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da za a nuna a ranar Lahadi, Scott Pelley, mai gabatar da shirin "60 Minutes", ya tambayi 'yan majalisa na Republican, John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham, ko FBI za ta iya samun wani abu da zai sa su canza ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya fi abokinsa na Carolina ta Kudu nuna gaskiya.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", Kennedy ya ce.
Na ce lokacin da shari'ar ta fara, na ce na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan an gabatar da tuhuma, na ce, "Ka yi wannan?"
Ya kasance mai ƙuduri, mai ƙarfi, mai ƙarfi.
Amma, ra'ayin Graham bai canja ba.
"Na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh, kuma zan bukaci wani babban zargi don canza shi", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta shi", in ji Graham, yana magana da Christine Blasey Ford.
Kuma duk wanda ta ambata sunansa ba zai iya tabbatar da hakan ba.
Wannan shari'ar ta shekara 36 da haihuwa.
Ba na ganin cewa wani sabon abu zai canza.
Mene ne bikin ƙauyuka na duniya, kuma shin ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
Za a gudanar da bikin Global Citizen Festival a ranar Asabar a birnin New York, wani biki ne na kiɗa da ake yi a kowace shekara, inda manyan taurari za su fito da manufofi masu tasiri iri ɗaya; don kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai da bikin, dubban mutane za su zo Central Park, ba kawai don sauraron waƙoƙin Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don jawo hankalin mutane game da ainihin manufar bikin, wato kawar da talauci a duniya nan da shekara ta 2030.
An kafa bikin ranar birane a shekara ta 2012 a matsayin wani ɓangare na shirin yaƙi da talauci a dukan duniya.
Don su samu tikiti kyauta (sai dai waɗanda suka biya kuɗin VIP), waɗanda suka halarci wannan liyafa suna bukatar su yi wasu ayyuka, kamar yin aikin sa kai, aika wa wani shugaban duniya imel, yin waya, ko kuma yin wasu abubuwa da suka dace don su taimaka wajen yaɗa bishara game da ƙarshen talauci.
Amma, da yake an yi shekara 12 ana wannan bikin, yaya aka yi nasarar?
Shin kyautar waƙoƙin kyauta hanya ce ta gaske ta lallashe mutane su yi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuwa kawai wani abu ne da ake kira "ƙaddamarwa" - inda mutane ke jin cewa suna yin wani abu mai mahimmanci ta hanyar sanya hannu kan jerin buƙatun kan layi ko aika saƙo akan Twitter?
Global Citizen ya ce tun daga shekarar 2011, ya samu sama da ayyuka miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa, domin kiran wasu manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce waɗannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawari da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 35 da za su shafi rayukan mutane fiye da biliyan 2.25 kafin shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta lissafa alkawura 390 da sanarwar saboda ayyukanta, wanda ya riga ya saka hannun jari ko ya tara aƙalla dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta ce har zuwa yanzu, kusan mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya sun amfana daga wannan kuɗin.
Wani babban alhakin ya fito ne daga The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya mai zuba jari da kuma gudanarwa a Birtaniya da ke aiki don "taimaka wa yara su more rayuwarsu", kuma ta yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa wajen kawo karshen matsalar karancin abinci a kasar, bayan da aka karbi sakonnin Twitter 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu tallafawa, gwamnatoci a duk duniya da kuma 'yan kasa kamar ku, za mu iya barin rashin adalci na zamantakewar da ake kira cin abinci a baya, Tracey Ullmann, wakilin The Power of Nutrition ya fadawa masu sauraro a wani biki a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an aika da takardun shaida 5,000 da ke nuna cewa ya kamata Birtaniya ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da tallafin wani shiri, Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 kuma ya samar musu da abinci mai gina jiki.
A cikin jerin tambayoyin da ake yawan yi a dandalinmu, akwai wata tambaya: Me ya sa kuke ganin za ku iya kawar da talauci?
Global Citizen ya amsa: Zai zama aiki mai tsawo da wahala - wani lokacin za mu kasa a kai a kai.
Amma, za mu kai ga iyakarmu, kamar yadda ƙungiyoyin kare haƙƙin ɗan adam da kuma kawar da nuna bambanci suka yi a gabanmu, domin muna da ƙarfi tare.
Wasu daga cikin masu gabatar da su a wannan shekara sun hada da Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, da Janelle Monáe.
Amurka na iya amfani da sojin ruwanta a matsayin "abin hanawa" don hana Rasha fitar da makamashi, in ji ministan cikin gida
"Idan ya zama dole, Washington na iya amfani da sojojin ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwanni, ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya", in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke, a cewar wani rahoto daga Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi iƙirarin cewa taimakon da Rasha ke bayarwa ga Siriya, musamman ma a matsayin mai aiki a ƙarƙashin gwamnatin da ke can, zai zama abin da za a iya amfani da shi don bincika sababbin kasuwanni.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke a Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne don su yi kasuwanci da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai da kudancinta", in ji shi, a cewar wasu majiyoyi.
Kuma, bisa ga sanarwar da aka yi, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin da za a iya magance shi.
Amurka na iya amfani da sojojin ruwa don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna budewa da kuma samar da shingayen ruwa idan ya cancanta, don tabbatar da cewa makamashi daga gare su baya shiga kasuwa,in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga baƙi a taron da aka shirya don Ƙungiyar Kula da Makamashi ta Masu Amfani, wata ƙungiya mai ba da agaji da ke kiran kanta "Muryar Masu Amfani da Makamashi" a Amirka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta yadda Washington ke tunkarar Rasha da Iran, ya ce sun yi kama.
Ya ce, "Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha shine rage amfani da albarkatun makamashi da maye gurbin su da wasu", ya ce, ya kuma ce Rasha tana da wasa daya ne kawai a zuciya da tattalin arzikin da ya dogara da man fetur.
Bayanan sun biyo bayan gwamnatin Trump na son kara yawan fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ta fi rahusa ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Don yin wannan, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaba Donald Trump da kansa, sun yi ƙoƙarin sa Jamus ta daina shiga cikin aikin "Nord Stream 2" na gina sabon layin wutar lantarki, wanda Trump ya ce zai sa Berlin ta zama "kurkuku" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta yi ta cewa aikin da ake kira Nord Stream 2 mai tsadar dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka ƙarfin da ake da shi yanzu zuwa wajen wajen wajen wajen biliyan 110 na murabba'in mita, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Rasha ta ce Washington ta yi tsayayya da wannan shiri ne saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma yana nuna rashin adalci.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa ba za a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki na matsa lamba ba kuma masu amfani da makamashi su zabi kayayyaki", inji ministan makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da ministan makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Kasar Jamus ta soki matakin da Amurka ta dauka, kuma ta tabbatar da cewa ta amince da wannan aikin.
Babban ƙungiyar masana'antu a Jamus, wato Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta yi kira ga Amirka da ta ci gaba da bin manufofin ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai da kuma yarjejeniyar da aka yi tsakanin birnin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina matukar jin takaicin yadda wasu kasashen waje ke cinye mana makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus, BDI, bayan ganawar da ya yi da Angela Merkel, shugabar gwamnatin Jamus, da Vladimir Putin, shugaban Rasha.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020, in ji ta
Elizabeth Warren, 'yar majalisar dattijai ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi la'akari da yin magana a taron gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu, kuma za mu bukaci mace a matsayin shugaba", in ji ta, a cewar wani rahoto daga The Hill.
Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da neman shugaban kasa.
Warren ya yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump a taron kuma ya ce yana "ja da kasar cikin hanyar da ba daidai ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai tsauraran ra'ayi game da sukar Trump da Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa "Tabbas dole ne mu sa FBI ta binciki lamarin kafin a kada kuri'a".
Amma kuma, wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa mafi yawan masu jefa kuri'a a lardin Warren ba sa ganin ya kamata ta yi takara a shekarar 2020.
Kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu son zabe a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata dan majalisar dattijai ya tsaya takara ba, a cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ta wallafa.
