Sauran shahararrun 'yan Democrat da aka yi wa magana game da yiwuwar neman takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020 sun hada da Joe Biden, tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa, da Bernie Sanders, dan majalisar dattijai daga Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance a watan Janairu, a cewar wani rahoton Associated Press.
