Sakataren Amurka ya zargi China da 'ta'addanci' ta hanyar 'yan leƙen asirin da aka yi
Mako guda bayan da wata jarida ta kasar Sin ta wallafa wasu tallace-tallace hudu a jaridar Amurka da ke nuna yadda cinikayya tsakanin kasashen biyu ke da amfani, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafafen yada labarai na Amurka wajen yada karya.
A ranar Laraba ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da tallan jaridar kasar Sin a jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa - bayan da ta zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Da'awar Trump cewa Beijing na son tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattijai na Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fadawa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne a cikin fadada yakin neman zabe na Washington don matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake baƙon gwamnati na iya yin tallace-tallace don ƙarfafa kasuwanci, amma Beijing da Washington suna faɗa cikin yaƙin kasuwanci, tare da sabon haraji a kan kayayyakin da suka shigo daga ƙasashen biyu.
Masana harkokin kasuwanci na kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce, an tsara takunkumin da kasar Sin ta dauka a farkon yakin cinikayya ne don cutar da bakin haure a jihohin da ke kusa da Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan jihar Iowa na dogon lokaci, wanda ke fitar da kayayyakin gona da yawa zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
Branstad ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a jaridar Des Moines Register cewa, "Kasar Sin tana kara tsananta wa kasar ta ta hanyar wallafa labaran karya a cikin 'yan jaridunmu".
"A cikin fadada wannan sanarwa, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da 'yancin fadin albarkacin baki da muke so da kuma 'yancin manema labarai ta hanyar buga wani talla mai tsada a jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad a cikin labarinsa.
"A gefe guda kuma, ba a samun wasu maganganun zanga-zanga a kan kantunan jaridu a titunan Beijing, kuma babu wani hakikanin tunani game da bambancin ra'ayi da Sinawa za su iya yi game da manufofin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, inda kafofin yada labarai ke karkashin mulkin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya daɗa cewa, "wani babban jarida a ƙasar Sin ya ƙi buga labarinsa, amma bai ambata jaridar ba".
