Mutumin da ya kirkiro intanet yana shirin kirkiro sabuwar intanet da zata yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, mutumin da ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya shirya kafa wani kamfani don yaƙi da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin da aka yi a baya bayan nan, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da Solid, wani dandamali ne na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da ke da izinin samun damar abin da bayanai.
A wata hira da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "ƙaddamar da duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi wannan yanzu", in ji shi game da kamfanin jirgin.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Wannan aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasaha daga Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu Kasuwancin Bayanai na Kan layi ko POD.
Za ka iya samun adireshin da ke cikin wannan dandalin da jerin abubuwan da kake son ka yi, kalandar aiki, littattafan kiɗa, da kuma wasu abubuwa da kake amfani da su a wurin aiki.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman game da adana bayanan sirri shine cewa yana da cikakken iko akan mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar abin da bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "zabin mutum ta hanyar amfani da bayanai".
A cewar John Bruce, shugaban kamfanin, manufar Inrupt ita ce kamfanin ya samar da kayan aiki, matakai da kuma ilimin da ya dace don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
A yau, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, mai sarrafa kayan tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu masu shirye-shirye da aka ɗauka a matsayin masu haɓaka don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shirye masu aikin sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a dukan duniya za su iya yin nasu aikace-aikacen ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su fara wani canji na gaba daya wanda zai juya tsarin kasuwancin su na yanzu sama da dare.
Ba ma tambayar su izini.
Berners-Lee ya rubuta a cikin wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar a Medium cewa Inrupt yana da  manufar samar da wutar lantarki a cikin kasuwancin da kuma yanayin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka gina akan Solid. 
Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a yanar gizo a 1994 lokacin da ya kafa Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin tattaunawar kan rashin daidaiton Intanet.
Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da zama wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban kungiyar World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar Gizo ta Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe, har ma a lokacin da ya kafa Inrupt.
