A shekara ta 1938, ambaliyar ruwa da ta addabi Donggala ta halaka mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
Ƙari ga haka, ambaliyar ruwa da ta auku a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996 ta kashe mutane tara.
