Ga manyan girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta auku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo ambaliyar ruwa da ta shafi ƙasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a duk faɗin gabar tekun Indiya, kuma kusan rabin mutanen a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu, an yi wata guguwa mai ƙarfi a yammacin ƙasar Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar teku na Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi girma a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta haddasa ambaliyar ruwa da ta addabi gabar teku ta kudu, ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta auku a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Western Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo ambaliyar ruwa mai tsawon kafa 10 da ta halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ta kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa da ta afkawa lardin Pidie Jaya a Aceh ta haddasa barna da tsoro. Mutane na tunawa da girgizar kasa da ambaliyar ruwa da ta auku a shekarar 2004.
Babu ambaliyar ruwa da aka kafa wannan lokaci, amma fiye da 100 ya mutu da gine-gine rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 9 da ɗari uku ta afka wa tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonisiya kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin
