An Kama Ɗan Dattijon Sarah Palin Bisa Zargi na Zalunci a Cikin Iyali
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar shugaban kasa, an kama shi da laifin cin zarafin mutum.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, a kan zargin aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, da kuma ƙoƙarin hana a kai rahoton aikata laifin da kuma yin tsayayya da kama, in ji rahoton 'yan sanda na Alaska da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa Palin ta ɗauki wayar abokinta sa'ad da take ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta sanar da laifin da ake nufi.
An tsare Palin a gidan yarin Mat-Su, inda ake jiran shari'a, kuma an ba shi belin dala 500, in ji rahoton KTUU.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu ranar Asabar inda ya bayyana cewa ba shi da laifi, mai tsauri lokacin da aka tambaye shi ko yana da laifi ko ba shi da laifi, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai.
Ana tuhumar Palin da laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin cewa za a iya yanke masa hukuncin daurin shekara guda a kurkuku da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake yi da ranar guda a kurkuku da kuma $2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka zargi Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an tuhume shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin ta kira 'yan sanda don sanar da kai hari.
Yanzu haka ana sauraron karar a kotun soja da ke jihar Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida, hana sanar da tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma dauke da makami a cikin abin da ya faru.
Budurwarsa ta ce ya buge ta a fuska.
