Masu gabatar da kara sun nemi a yankewa wani da ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun bukaci a yankewa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da hannu a harin ta'addanci a birnin New York da ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar domin karya dokar tarayya tun 1953.
An yi zargin Saipov, mai shekara 30, da hayar wata motar Home Depot don kai hari kan masu hawan keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da keke a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni da gangan, a cewar sanarwar da aka yi a kotu a gundumar kudu ta New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan zarge-zargen za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa, a cewar rahoton.
Makonni da yawa bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov a kan wasu abubuwa 22, ciki har da wasu abubuwa takwas da ake tuhuma da su na kisan kai, wanda ake amfani da shi a lokacin da ake tuhumar masu gabatar da kara da kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya kunshi "shirye-shiryen da aka shirya", kuma sun bayyana ayyukan Sapiov a matsayin "mummunan, munanan, da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya mutu sanadiyyar raunin da ya yi wa danginsa da abokansa Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
Wadanda aka kashe biyar daga cikin su 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da Kudancin New York ya yi shari'ar kisa.
An tuhumi wanda ake tuhuma Khalid Barnes da laifin kashe wasu masu shan miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
An yi hukuncin kisa a New York a shekara ta 1953 a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an tuhume su da yin leƙen asiri ga Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe ma'auratan a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wanda aka haifa a Uzbekistan, bai nuna alamar tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa jami'an bincike cewa yana baƙin ciki sosai don abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu ra'ayin kai harin ne bayan da ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar karar.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna masa tutar ISIS a dakin jinya, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya bayyana rashin laifinsa a dukkan bangarorin 22 na tuhumar.
David Patton, daya daga cikin jami'an tsaro na Saipov, ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da ake yi wa masu gabatar da kara.
Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon amincewa da hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar samun damar sakewa ba, zai kara haifar da mummunan sakamako ga duk wanda ya shafi lamarin, in ji Patton.
A baya, lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
