Ƙungiyar 'yan wasa ta Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci wa Giants kwallo biyu a wasan da suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun gyara rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Elite ta Ingila da suka sha a ranar Juma'a a kan Belfast Giants, ta hanyar lashe wasan da suka buga a ranar Asabar, 5-3 a Dundee.
Giants sun samu ci biyu a raga bayan da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka ci gaba da buga musu kwallo.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita a wasan gida, amma Dwyer ya sake kaiwa Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita da Dundee kuma kwallo biyu daga Lukas Lundvald Nielsen sun tabbatar da nasarar su.
