Dalilin da yasa yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
Farkon harbi a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya kasance mai ban sha'awa, kuma ko da yake har yanzu ba a gama yakin ba, ƙwararrun masana sun ce, hakan zai iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara harbi a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminum.
Babban matakin da aka dauka a wannan makon shi ne sabon harajin da aka saka kan kayayyaki masu darajar dala biliyan 200 (fam biliyan 150) kuma ya sanya haraji kan kusan rabin kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta amsa da wannan furucin a kowane lokaci, kwanan nan ta saka haraji na kashi 5 zuwa 10 bisa ɗari a kan kayayyakin Amirka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
Saboda haka, kasar Sin ta yi ta nuna rashin amincewa da harajin da Amurka ta saka, kuma ba za ta yi saurin barin kasar da ta fi karfin tattalin arziki a duniya ba.
Don samun Washington ta yi watsi da bukatar, amma zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin ya yi watsi da Amurka a fili.
Amma, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi nasara, matsin lamba daga yaƙin cinikayya da Amirka zai iya shafan kasar Sin a nan gaba, ta wajen rage bukatar tattalin arzikin biyu.
Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara kan siyasa da sauri a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da koma bayan tattalin arziki a kowace ƙasa, hakika ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka yarda a baya, in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike wanda ya fi mayar da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta New American.
Sashen Harkokin Wajen Syria Ya Ce A Shirye Yake Don Ceto 'Yan Gudun Hijira
Kasar Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijirar da son ransu kuma suna neman taimako don sake gina ƙasar da ta lalace bayan yaƙi na shekara bakwai.
Walid al Moualem, ministan harkokin wajen kasar ya yi jawabi a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ya ce yanayin kasar na samun sauki.
Ya ce, "a yau, yanayin duniya ya fi karko da tsaro, saboda nasarar da aka samu wajen yaki da ta'addanci".
Gwamnati ta ci gaba da kawo yanayin da ya dace ta hanyar gina wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka yi ta'addanci.
Yanzu an shirya wa 'yan gudun hijirar su koma ƙasarsu da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma tattalin arziki da ke shafar rayuwarsu da kuma ayyukansu.
Hukumar ta ce 'yan Syria sama da miliyan biyar ne suka gudu daga kasar tun lokacin da aka soma yaƙi a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke cikin ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce hukumomin Syria za su yi farin cikin karbar taimako wajen sake gina kasar.
Amma ya nanata cewa ba za su karɓi taimako na kan kari ko kuma daga ƙasashen da suka goyi bayan tawaye ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta Paris
Tawagar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta hanyar doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin wasa na Le Golf National a wajen birnin Paris na Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta sha kaye sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Ƙasar Turai ta sake lashe gasar, sa'ad da tawagar, wadda dan Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya ja-gora, ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata don ta doke Amirka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya fi fama da wahala a gasar, ya buga kwallo ta farko a cikin ruwa a rami na 16, wanda shine par 3, ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Molinari dan wasan Italiya ya yi wasa a duk wasanninsa, ya zama 1 cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka ci 5-0-0, tun lokacin da gasar ta fara amfani da tsarinta na yanzu a 1979.
Jordan Spieth na Amurka ya sha kashi 5 da 4 a hannun Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark, amma ya kasance a baya a cikin jerin 'yan wasan Turai.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ke kan gaba a jerin 'yan wasan golf mafi kyau a duniya, ya sha kashi 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya buga gasar cin kofin Ryder ta karshe.
Sergio Garcia na Spain, wanda ya buga gasar Ryder Cup sau takwas, ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara a gasar tare da 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
