Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan kwallon kafa a tarihi, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni 14 kuma na biyu ne kawai ga Jack Nicklaus.
